    <releases>
        <release version="2021.7.28-treviso" date="2021-07-28">
          <description>
            <ul>
                <li>Support for .lnk files</li>
                <li>Run any .exe/.msi/.lnk using the flags -e/-l in command line</li>
                <li>Specify the target bottle using the -b flag in command line</li>
                <li>Run executables without show the Bottles Window</li>
                <li>Dependencies can now set register keys</li>
                <li>Dependencies can now extract archives</li>
                <li>Dependencies can now uninstall other dependencies</li>
                <li>Dependencies can now install more dll in one step</li>
                <li>Dependencies can now register fonts in the Bottle Register to make them discoverable by the runner</li>
                <li>Cab extraction now support wildcards</li>
                <li>Cab extraction now support lowercase extensions</li>
                <li>When installing a new runner, winemenubuilder is blocked to prevent the creation of broken desktop entries</li>
                <li>The bottle root is now set as the working directory for all executed commands</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug in the dependency manager showing them installed even though the process was still running</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug that prevented states from being sent to the bottle (kill, shutdown, reboot, ..)</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug on processes listing</li>
                <li>Fix crash log path on Flatpak</li>
                <li>Fixed an issue causing Bottles to detect downloaded dxvk even when it fails</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug that cause some programs to not be placed in Programs section</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug that cause Bottles to crash when a component download fail</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug in adding registry keys with spaces in name</li>
                <li>Uninstallers are now no longer displayed in the Programs list</li>
                <li>Disable uninstaller button for dependencies installed from cab files</li>
                <li>Access Bottles preferences from the bottle creation view</li>
                <li>A spinner is now displayed when installing dependencies, programs and components</li>
                <li>Warning for missing cabextract tool</li>
                <li>Warning for experimental features</li>
                <li>Warning for enables testing repository</li>
                <li>Several improvements in runner management</li>
                <li>Added icons to the sidebar</li>
                <li>Experimantal support for Bottles installers</li>
                <li>Better support for Breeze theme</li>
                <li>Browse programs path</li>
                <li>Generate Bottles compatible desktop entries for programs installed trought Bottles installers</li>
                <li>Visual feedback during a state restoring</li>
                <li>Add external executable to the program list</li>
                <li>Toggle update date on bottles list</li>
                <li>Chinese (Simplified) translations thanks to @Yuzaihhhh and @sr093906</li>
                <li>Japanese translations thanks to @jatin-cbs</li>
                <li>Hungarian translations thanks to @ovari</li>
                <li>Polish translations thanks to Krzysztof Marcinek</li>
                <li>French translations thanks to @julroy67</li>
                <li>Russian translations thanks to @tacitcoast</li>
                <li>Italian translations thanks to @blackcat-917</li>
            </ul>
          </description>
        </release>
